@Ade2unge @rstats_tweets between doesn't work with datetime, but {lubridate} can help #RStats

library(lubridate)
set.seed(1)

last_month <- ymd(20211015) - 0:29

df <- tibble::tibble(
  date = last_month,
  price = runif(30)
)

dplyr::filter(df, date %within% interval(ymd(20210925), ymd(20211005)))
